long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: IskoDuler is the perfect tool to help you efficiently select your classes during pre-enlistment. It shows you the probability of getting each subject so you can correctly prioritize your rankings, and properly select which class to take.
